-- ALTER VIEW kpiemail.dim_painel_medico
-- as
SELECT
     [CRM_CICLO]
,[MES]
,[CICLO]
,[CRM]
,[MEDICO]
,[TIPO]
,[TIPOCONTATO]
,[GRUPOPROMOCIONAL]
,[ESPECIALIDADE]
,[LOGRADOURO]
,[COMPLEMENTO]
,[BAIRRO]
,[CIDADE]
,[UF]
,[CEP]
,[BRICK]
,[TELEFONEMEDICO]
,[CELULARMEDICO]
,[EMAIL_1_1]
,[ROW_ID_FUNCIONARIO]
,[ROW_ID_TERRITORIO]
,[ROW_ID_CONTATO]
,[STATUS]
,[QTD_VISITA_PLANEJADA_PAINEL]
,[QTD_VISITA_REALIZADA_PAINEL]
,[ESPECIALIDADE_02]
,[ESPECIALIDADE_03]
,[VP_PROX]
,[STATUS_MEDICO]
,[EMAIL_1_1_CONSENT]
,[NETWORK_ID]
,[RX_GIGYA_ID]
,[VEEVA_ID]
,[ROW_ID_CONTATO_EXT]
,[EMAIL_MASS]
,[EMAIL_MASS_CONSENT]
,[CYCLE_PLAN]
,[MERCADO]
,[PRODUTO_PAINEL]
,[KEY_TERR_CONT_CICLO]
,[KEY_TERR_CICLO]
,[KEY_CICLO_CRM]
,[DATE_KEY]
FROM
    OPENROWSET(
        BULK 'https://gsksynapseaccount.dfs.core.windows.net/gskoutputfiles/Email & KPI Visitacao/dimensao_painel_medico_*.parquet',
        FORMAT='PARQUET'
    ) WITH (
        [CRM_CICLO]             			VARCHAR(250) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[MES]                              VARCHAR(250) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[CICLO]                            VARCHAR(250) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[CRM]                              VARCHAR(250) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[MEDICO]                           VARCHAR(250) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[TIPO]                             VARCHAR(250) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[TIPOCONTATO]                      VARCHAR(250) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[GRUPOPROMOCIONAL]                 VARCHAR(250) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[ESPECIALIDADE]                    VARCHAR(250) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[LOGRADOURO]                       VARCHAR(250) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[COMPLEMENTO]                      VARCHAR(250) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[BAIRRO]                           VARCHAR(250) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[CIDADE]                           VARCHAR(250) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[UF]                               VARCHAR(250) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[CEP]                              VARCHAR(250) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[BRICK]                            VARCHAR(250) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[TELEFONEMEDICO]                   VARCHAR(250) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[CELULARMEDICO]                    VARCHAR(250) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[EMAIL_1_1]                        VARCHAR(250) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[ROW_ID_FUNCIONARIO]               VARCHAR(250) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[ROW_ID_TERRITORIO]                VARCHAR(250) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[ROW_ID_CONTATO]                   VARCHAR(250) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[STATUS]                           VARCHAR(250) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[QTD_VISITA_PLANEJADA_PAINEL]      VARCHAR(250) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[QTD_VISITA_REALIZADA_PAINEL]      VARCHAR(250) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[ESPECIALIDADE_02]                 VARCHAR(250) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[ESPECIALIDADE_03]                 VARCHAR(250) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[VP_PROX]                          VARCHAR(250) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[STATUS_MEDICO]                    VARCHAR(250) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[EMAIL_1_1_CONSENT]                VARCHAR(250) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[NETWORK_ID]                       VARCHAR(250) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[RX_GIGYA_ID]                      VARCHAR(250) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[VEEVA_ID]                         VARCHAR(250) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[ROW_ID_CONTATO_EXT]               VARCHAR(250) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[EMAIL_MASS]                       VARCHAR(250) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[EMAIL_MASS_CONSENT]               VARCHAR(250) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[CYCLE_PLAN]                       VARCHAR(250) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[MERCADO]                          VARCHAR(250) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[PRODUTO_PAINEL]                   VARCHAR(250) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[KEY_TERR_CONT_CICLO]              VARCHAR(250) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[KEY_TERR_CICLO]                   VARCHAR(250) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[KEY_CICLO_CRM]					VARCHAR(250) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[DATE_KEY]  DATE ) AS ROW
